    v2 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.12 / v1 + 0.19)) / ((v2 + 0.12 * v2 + 0.99) * wp.exp(v0 + 0.95)))
    v0 = ((tmp - 0.52) * 0.65)
    v0 = v2
    tmp = tmp
    v2 = 0.74

    v2 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.73 + v2 + 0.01)) / wp.sin(wp.abs(v0 + 0.38)))
